    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were assessed with achieved levels below required levels; six factors were flagged as epistemic gaps. The Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification framework provides sufficient confidence in the hemolysis predictions for regulatory submission purposes. The assessment team concludes that the model credibility is adequate for the intended use.",
